1360
01:19:56.988 --> 01:20:00.168
The five-year survival rate is only around 3%,

1361
01:20:01.368 --> 01:20:05.287
highlighting an urgent need to understand the unique mechanisms

1362
01:20:05.368 --> 01:20:09.248
of the metastatic TME to develop effective therapies.

1363
01:20:11.228 --> 01:20:15.028
In primary pancreatic cancer, tumor-associated macrophages,

1364
01:20:15.428 --> 01:20:18.728
TAMs, play important role in inflammation and

1365
01:20:18.908 --> 01:20:21.148
