1366
01:20:22.848 --> 01:20:26.508
Pancreatic cancer is known as an immunologically cold tumor

1367
01:20:26.688 --> 01:20:30.618
with low T cell infiltration and fibrosis is

1368
01:20:30.708 --> 01:20:32.848
