1384
01:21:29.448 --> 01:21:30.028
and effect.

1385
01:21:30.828 --> 01:21:34.467
In addition, this analysis is based on primary

1386
01:21:34.508 --> 01:21:34.848
tumor,

1387
01:21:35.668 --> 01:21:38.968
and the role of interferon gamma in metastatic

1388
01:21:39.048 --> 01:21:40.948
environments remains unclear.

1389
01:21:42.808 --> 01:21:46.728
To address this, I reanalyzed the public human single-cell

1390
01:21:46.908 --> 01:21:49.868
RNA seq data from untreated liver metastasis.

1391
01:21:51.588 --> 01:21:55.548
I found that interferon gamma was mainly expressed by

1392
01:21:55.588 --> 01:21:56.938
T and NK cells,

1393
01:21:57.828 --> 01:22:01.638
while interferon gamma R2 was highly enriched

1394
01:22:01.708 --> 01:22:04.828
in myeloid cells, especially macrophages.

1395
01:22:05.738 --> 01:22:09.708
Therefore, in this study, I aim to clarify the role of

1396
01:22:09.828 --> 01:22:13.738
macrophage-specific interferon gamma signaling in pancreatic

1397
01:22:13.738 --> 01:22:16.808
cancer liver metastasis using a multi-omics analysis.

1398
01:22:19.908 --> 01:22:23.328
Our lab established a liver metastasis model by

1399
01:22:23.408 --> 01:22:26.268
injecting pancreatic cancer cells into the portal vein.

1400
01:22:27.668 --> 01:22:31.648
First, systemic interferon gamma blockade using a neutralizing

1401
01:22:31.768 --> 01:22:35.608
antibody significantly increased both tumor number

1402
01:22:35.628 --> 01:22:36.628
and tumor burden.

1403
01:22:38.128 --> 01:22:41.368
Flow cytometric analysis showed an increase in

1404
01:22:41.388 --> 01:22:45.328
TAMs and reduced expression of CD80 and

1405
01:22:45.468 --> 01:22:46.468
CD86,

1406
01:22:47.308 --> 01:22:49.588
which are well-known costimulatory molecules.

1407
01:22:50.928 --> 01:22:54.688
However, I saw no significant changes in T cell function.

1408
01:22:56.148 --> 01:22:59.648
These results suggest that interferon gamma regulates

1409
01:22:59.728 --> 01:23:03.528
