1414
01:23:16.608 --> 01:23:19.388
using interferon gamma R2 flox LysM-Cre.

1415
01:23:21.188 --> 01:23:24.328
In bone marrow-derived macrophages from these mice,

1416
01:23:25.188 --> 01:23:28.568
interferon gamma R2 expression and PSTAT1

1417
01:23:28.648 --> 01:23:32.288
signaling were significantly reduced, confirming

1418
01:23:32.448 --> 01:23:33.608
