1431
01:24:25.228 --> 01:24:27.748
This change also affected T cells.

1432
01:24:28.608 --> 01:24:31.548
In knockout mice, the number of

1433
01:24:31.588 --> 01:24:35.368
Ki67-positive CD4 and CD8 T

1434
01:24:35.448 --> 01:24:36.608
cells were reduced,

1435
01:24:37.708 --> 01:24:41.208
along with interferon gamma and TNF alpha production.

1436
01:24:42.488 --> 01:24:46.368
This suggests that interferon gamma signaling in myeloid cells

1437
01:24:46.468 --> 01:24:48.308
