1438
01:24:49.588 --> 01:24:53.028
To better understand these global changes in the tumor

1439
01:24:53.108 --> 01:24:56.338
microenvironment, we performed a bulk RNA seq

1440
01:24:56.588 --> 01:24:57.208
analysis.

1441
01:24:59.668 --> 01:25:03.068
Interferon gamma hallmark signaling was significantly

1442
01:25:03.108 --> 01:25:04.978
