1445
01:25:14.028 --> 01:25:15.008
ECM remodeling.

1446
01:25:16.048 --> 01:25:19.928
In contrast, immune-related pathways such as T cell

1447
01:25:19.968 --> 01:25:22.588
immunity and antigen presentation were reduced.

1448
01:25:23.728 --> 01:25:27.688
These results suggest that loss of interferon gamma signaling shifts

1449
01:25:27.708 --> 01:25:30.268
the tumor microenvironment from an

1450
01:25:30.308 --> 01:25:34.148
inflammatory to a fibrotic and immunosuppressive

1451
01:25:34.288 --> 01:25:38.152
stateHowever, bulk RNA-seq does not

1452
01:25:38.172 --> 01:25:41.832
allow us to identify which cell types are responsible for these

1453
01:25:41.912 --> 01:25:45.252
changes. Therefore, we performed single-cell

1454
01:25:45.332 --> 01:25:46.592
RNA-seq analysis.

1455
01:25:49.212 --> 01:25:52.892
Comparing our mouse single-cell RNA-seq with the human data,

1456
01:25:54.172 --> 01:25:57.872
we confirmed that interferon gamma mild axis is highly

1457
01:25:57.992 --> 01:25:58.632
conserved.

1458
01:25:59.952 --> 01:26:03.692
In both species, interferon gamma is produced by

1459
01:26:03.732 --> 01:26:07.232
